adise after punishment","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Salamah ibn Nu\u2019aym reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever meets Allah without associating any partners with Him will eventually enter Paradise.\u201d I said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery and theft?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery and theft.\u201d Source: al-Sunnah li-Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6663,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/19\/grand-petty-theft\/","url_meta":{"origin":6653,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Thieves: Cutting the hand applied to grand theft, not petty theft","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The hand of the thief was never cut in the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, for what is less than the price of a shield or piece of armor, and both of them were expensive. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6408, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1824,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/12\/allah-torture-punish\/","url_meta":{"origin":6653,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Torture: Allah will punish those who torture people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 12